00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:09,461
Middle East oil and LNG producers are continuing loadings despite recent attacks on ships and rising tension near key sea routes.

2
00:00:09,411 --> 00:00:15,145
Traders are watching insurance costs, vessel availability and possible delays.

3
00:00:15,145 --> 00:00:24,261
For energy buyers, the main risk is not only price volatility but also whether shipping confidence can hold if threats continue.

